In (Wang et al., 2017), the ideality factor of the diode, the slope of the I–V curve at the OC point, and the SC point are all picked at random

Huang et. al. (2011)
Maximum power point, SC point, OC point, and maximum power point’s power derivative with respect to voltage are all set to zero

